    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm a high school civics teacher and I'm planning a lesson on the 14th Amendment. I want to focus on the concept of 'substantive due process' and how it has been used to protect civil rights and personal liberties. Can you draft a clear explanation I can use for my students that highlights these protections?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
